{"tid":565853,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【大師啟示】沈大師為港股求得上上籤 騰訊下下籤！","createTime":"2018-02-19T11:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T11:22:49.000Z","uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eeebb6ff09d52196d1bb32ba949d26e5f37bf38d","tid":565853,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T11:22:49.000Z","msg":"港股　《第七十三靈籤：孫霖中狀元》<br />\n<br />\n求籤吉凶：上上靈籤<br />\n算命籤詩：<br />\n<br />\n夾道花香襯馬蹄 藍袍改換錦衣歸<br />\n滿街紅粉皆爭羨 翹首芳名雁塔題<br />\n<br />\n佛隱居士解說：<br />\n港股於過咗7月後或會見高位，但預料今年港股表現大起大跌，籲股民勿高追。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n騰訊（700）第六十一靈籤：十二金牌召岳飛<br />\n<br />\n求籤吉凶：下下靈籤<br />\n算命籤詩：<br />\n<br />\n十二金牌速召回 奸雄設計幾時灰<br />\n可憐一旦功勞散 老少扶車不斷哀<br />\n<br />\n佛隱居士解說：<br />\n騰訊表現起落大，籲股民勿高追。一旦摸頂高追，有機會成副身家「功勞散」，即係輸晒成副身家呀！小心小心！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180219/57847465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57847465&d=vmKD4W8mTms%2Fq90gnFo94iwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f0db460c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57847465&h=829564e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180219/57847465</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}